text: Anonidium is a genus of plant in family Annonaceae. It contains the following species: * Anonidium brieyi Engl. & Diels * Anonidium le-testui Pellegr. * Anonidium floribundum Pellegr. * Anonidium mannii Engl. & Diels \- junglesop * Anonidium usambarense R.E.
